nd blessings be upon him, than anyone before me. I have not seen anyone more lenient in living, nor less harsh than them.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24178,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/14\/daughters-precious-companions\/","url_meta":{"origin":33124,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Daughters: Your daughters are precious companions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not hate your daughters, for they are your precious companions.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 17373 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064f\u0643\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0647\u064f\u0648\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/331